Run:
You need Scala 2.8... then run ./bashbeans -r
On Windows you also need cygwin, and you run with ./bashbeans -r --cygwin

Keys:
Arrow keys ... move
Space ... shoot
LCTRL ... reload
RCTRL ... stop

Q->R ... translate/rotate X
A->F ... translate/rotate Y
Y->V ... translate/rotate Z

T ... become a tree
1,2, ... tree display mode